arts.ttl: KNVB Cup: Go Ahead Eagles stun PSV to reach the final
arts.sum: Go Ahead Eagles have reached the KNVB Cup final after a shock 2-1 win over PSV Eindhoven. PSV controlled the game from the start but two goals within two minutes stunned the hosts. Firstly, Gerrit Nauber headed in a corner after 25 minutes before Victor Edvardsen netted from a swift counter to make it 2-0. arts.ttl: Liverpool draw PSG, Arsenal face PSV, Villa meet Club Brugge in last 16
arts.sum: Liverpool will face Paris St-Germain in the Champions League last-16, while Arsenal take on PSV Eindhoven and Aston Villa will play Club Brugge.
